parameters: The place looks pungent compared to Lont.
When I hated something at first, even if I didn't
really hate it at the end I couldn't quite like it.
I never felt anything like that.
That's cus you're a shallow guy.
exactly make a great one in our meeting.
Because I think of you as an important friend.
Let's do our best in the future, too.
I never really liked you that much anyway.
Let's search for information on Certilt's
Lord of Reason while walking, too.
Not even collecting information, is there
even anyone in this forest who can talk?
A type of monster. A Dryad, they say.
粉砕エフェクトを指定
But if so, this shouldn't happen either...
It's strange no matter which way you look at it.
A Dryad in this state... is unheard of.
This is nothing but an anomaly!
Yeah, but like, what ARE you?
I didn't ask for your name...
You know something about the Dryad earlier,
I don't know, so I'm looking into it.
Are you buddies with the Dryads, or something?
Other species also live there, too.
Is that town close to here, perhaps?
I'm also going back home, so...
We must also collect information on the way.
Hey, little thingy, guide us there.
